# Folder Overview
- films_tmdb.csv
- tmdb.ipynb
- Output folder

# File Description
- films_tmdb.csv: Contains list of film titles and their corresponding tmdb id. The list of films was pulled from the list of nomimees and winners of the Academy Awards from 1996-2024 for the following categories: Directing, Actor in a Leading Role, Actor in a Supporting Role, Actress in a Leading Role, Actress in a Supporting Role, and Best Picture. TMDB id's were manually inputed from the TMDB website, https://www.themoviedb.org/?language=en-US. 
- tmdb.ipynb: Fetches data from TMDB API, processes film credits and detail. Python version 3.13.9. Jupyterlab version 4.4.7. 
- Output folder: Contains all the outputs from tmdb.ipynb, including multiple versions
